fn.p:
pi:
population at the origin (L: livestock, H: human);
pj: population at destination (L: livestock, H: human); dij: distance (g: great circle distance, a: costhpath distance based on accessibility friction surface, el: costhpath distance based on elevation friction surface), mode: transport modality (by truck or on foot).

